Author: TheMilkierMan
Text: I feel so bad when my mom bakes for me and she's like "why aren't you eating, are they not good?" And I'm like omg no, they're amazing my brain's just telling me that if I eat a single cookie I'll gain 40lbs and die (thank you for thinking of me though)

Author: taoshka
Text: Dude, same. I'm hormonal and I've eaten an embarrassing amount of cookies today :/
